Each user can also check the status of three other people who are using it.
When a potential danger is detected, the app not only recommends self-quarantine, but it also alerts local health officials. Big data analytics on cellphone data, facial recognition technology, mobile phone tracking and artificial intelligence are used to track infected people and the people they have contacted in South Korea, Taiwan and Singapore.
